headline: Prologis price target lowered to $124 from $132 at Jefferies
summary: Jefferies lowered the firm’s price target on Prologis (PLD) to $124 from $132 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm updated its analysis of real estate investment trusts on the U.S. manufacturing “boom” and its positive impacts on warehouse demand. President-elect Trump won’t hinder the Biden stimulus for manufacturing, and tariffs, or their threat, will drive U.S. companies to invest domestically, the analyst tells investors in a research note. Jefferies upgraded EastGroup (EGP) to a B
